    <title>&lt;b&gt;Best of Flaschenpost - Teil 1&lt;b&gt;</title>
    <description>&lt;div class=&quot;bild-links&quot;&gt; &lt;img src=&quot;http://kef.podspot.de/files/hausstrand.jpg&quot; size=&quot;41919&quot; /&gt; 
